01:48:17.300 --> 01:48:19.900
I'm trying to find
the right thing to say.

01:48:24.000 --> 01:48:26.400
I think if the obvious response...

01:48:26.600 --> 01:48:29.200
...doesn't immediately
come to you, we can...

01:48:30.500 --> 01:48:32.000
...just...

