Thank you, thank you.

02:01:16.000 --> 02:01:17.300
I'm...

02:01:17.500 --> 02:01:20.900
I'm absolutely overwhelmed...

02:01:21.800 --> 02:01:23.400
...that I could climb those stairs.

02:01:24.800 --> 02:01:25.700
He did great.

